trans-unit.source: Specifies a date and time associated with the type library of an ActiveX control hosted by an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Especifica uma data e hora associadas à biblioteca de tipos de um controle ActiveX hospedado por um controle <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DateTime" /> value representing the date and time to associate with the type library.
trans-unit.target: Um valor <see cref="T:System.DateTime" /> que representa a data e a hora a serem associadas à biblioteca de tipos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.TypeLibraryTimeStampAttribute" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost.TypeLibraryTimeStampAttribute" />.

trans-unit.source: The date and time to associate with the type library.
trans-unit.target: A data e a hora a serem associadas à biblioteca de tipos.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DateTime" /> value representing the date and time to associate with the type library.
trans-unit.target: Um valor <see cref="T:System.DateTime" /> que representa a data e a hora a serem associadas à biblioteca de tipos.
